---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Affiliate Disclosure — CalcTax"
  description="How CalcTax earns revenue through affiliate partnerships while keeping all calculators free."
>
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 prose">
    <h1>Affiliate Disclosure</h1>

    <p>
      CalcTax is a free tax calculator website. We earn revenue through affiliate partnerships,
      which means we may receive a commission when you sign up for a product or service through
      a link on our site. This comes at no extra cost to you.
    </p>

    <h2>How This Works</h2>
    <p>
      After you use our calculators, we may recommend products that are relevant to your
      situation — such as tax filing software. If you click through and sign up, the company
      pays us a referral fee. This is how we keep our calculators free and ad-free.
    </p>

    <h2>Our Partners</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Wealthsimple Tax</strong> — Free tax filing software for Canadians</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Our Commitment</h2>
    <p>
      Affiliate partnerships do not influence our calculator results. Your tax calculations
      are based solely on CRA-published rates and your inputs. We only recommend products
      we believe are genuinely useful.
    </p>

    <h2>Questions?</h2>
    <p>
      If you have questions about our affiliate relationships, contact us at
      <a href="/contact">our contact page</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</Base>
